#. (itstool) path: component/name
#: org.kde.plasma.iconexplorer.appdata.xml:8
msgid "Icon Explorer"
msgstr "Icon Explorer ( Explorator de icone) "

#. (itstool) path: component/summary
#: org.kde.plasma.iconexplorer.appdata.xml:9
msgid "Icon Previewer for Artists and Developers"
msgstr "Monstrator preliminar de icone per artistas e disveloppatores"

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.plasma.iconexplorer.appdata.xml:11
msgid ""
"Icon Explorer allows artists and developers to preview and pick icons. Icon "
"Explorer attempts to render the icons exactly as they would look drawn in "
"the application. It allows to filter based on category and name. Icon "
"Explorer is not a general-purpose tool, but geared towards artists' and "
"developers' use-cases. Icon Explorer also provides a plugin for Kate and "
"KDevelop to be used as icon picker."
msgstr ""
"Icon Explorer (Explorator de Icone) permitte a artistas e disveloppatores "
"previsualizar e colliger icones. Icon Explorer essaya render le icones "
"exactemente como illes deberea semblar designate in le application. Il "
"permitte filtrar basate sur categorias e nomine. Icon explorer non es un "
"instrumento de uso general,ma orientate per casos de usator de artistas e "
"disveloppatores. Icon explorer anque forni un pluigin per Kate e Kdevelop "
"que pote esser usate como colligitor de icone. "
